Package model

Class NameList

java.lang.Object
model.NameList
public class NameList extends Object
Represents a singly linked list for storing names in alphabetical order. This class provides methods to insert, remove, search for, and manage names while maintaining the sorted order of the list.

The list maintains both head and tail references for efficient operations at both ends and ensures names are always stored in alphabetical order.

2024
